            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-07-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-10-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="556" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d556">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For text of a letter from President Truman to Enrico de Nicola, Provisional
                    President of the Italian Republic, upon the occasion of De Gasperi’s departure
                    from the United States, see <hi rend="italic">Public Papers of the Presidents of
                        the United States: Harry S. Truman, 1947</hi>, page 105. The letter, dated
                    January 20, was released on January 25.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
